SKILL|yuanbao|"Yuanbao (元宝) groups: @mention users, query info/members."
STEP|1|Your text reply IS the message sent to the group/user.** The gateway automatically delivers your response text to the chat. You do NOT need any special "send message" tool — just reply normally and it
STEP|2|NEVER say you cannot send messages or @mention users. NEVER suggest the user do it manually. NEVER add disclaimers about permissions. Just reply with the text you want sent.**
STEP|3|Call `yb_query_group_members` with `action="find"`, `name="<target name>"`, `mention=true`
STEP|4|Get the exact nickname from the response
STEP|5|Include `@nickname` in your reply text — the gateway handles the rest
STEP|6|That's it.** No extra explanation needed. Keep it short and natural.
STEP|7|Rules:**
STEP|8|Call `yb_query_group_members` first to get the exact nickname — do NOT guess
STEP|9|The @mention format: `@nickname` with a space before the @ sign
STEP|10|Your reply text IS the message — it WILL be sent and the @mention WILL work
STEP|11|Be concise. Do NOT explain how @mention works to the user.
STEP|12|Call `yb_send_dm` with `group_code`, `name` (target user's name), and `message`
STEP|13|The tool automatically finds the user and sends the DM
STEP|14|Report the result to the user
STEP|15|Rules:**
STEP|16|Extract `group_code` from the current chat_id (e.g. `group:535168412` → `535168412`)
STEP|17|If you already know the user_id, pass it directly via the `user_id` parameter to skip lookup
STEP|18|If multiple users match the name, the tool returns candidates — ask the user to clarify
STEP|19|Do NOT use `send_message` tool for Yuanbao DMs — use `yb_send_dm` instead
STEP|20|Supports media: images (.jpg/.png/.gif/.webp/.bmp) sent as image messages, other files as documents
STEP|21|`group_code` comes from chat_id: `group:328306697` → `328306697`
STEP|22|Groups are called "派 (Pai)" in the Yuanbao app
STEP|23|Member roles: `user`, `yuanbao_ai`, `bot`
